  <!-- EN: "Longyuan Thundercore" EML turret -->
  <CMC_EMcannon.label>HPJ-06 45mm电磁炮</CMC_EMcannon.label>
  <!-- EN: A heavy electro-magnetic launcher mounted on a turret capable of firing 76mm anti-vehicle shell. Its large-caliber projectiles do heavy damage over significant ranges, and causing various EMP bursts upon hit.\n\nTurret rotation speed: 60°/sec. -->
  <CMC_EMcannon.description>HPJ-06型45mm自动电磁炮「龙渊·雷枢」，其发射的大口径射弹可以在远距离重创目标，接触时附带EMP效果。</CMC_EMcannon.description>
