  <CMC_EMcannon.comps.CompRefuelable.outOfFuelMessage>需要更换炮管</CMC_EMcannon.comps.CompRefuelable.outOfFuelMessage>
  
  <!-- EN: "Longyuan Thunderstrike"130mm EML -->
  <CMC_EMcannon_Huge.label>HPJ-1X 130mm电磁舰炮</CMC_EMcannon_Huge.label>
  <!-- EN: Serving as standardized armament for interstellar merchant vessels and destroyers, this naval gun launches 30+ Mach guided projectiles capable of instantly vaporizing targets. However, the absence of large-caliber shipborne capacitor systems results in significantly constrained rates of fire and turret traverse speeds. -->
  <CMC_EMcannon_Huge.description>作为星际商船与驱逐舰的标准化武装，HPJ-1X型130mm电磁舰炮「龙渊·镇海」发射的30马赫级制导炮弹可瞬间击碎重甲目标，极高的初速也可使其将炮弹发射入低轨道进行洲际打击。但因缺乏大口径舰载电容系统，导致射速与炮塔转向速率显著受限。</CMC_EMcannon_Huge.description>
  <!-- EN: Barrel durability -->
